title: Natalie Roser soaks up the sun by poolside in Los Angeles

text:
She split from her personal trainer fianc√© Dan Adair last October and is rumoured to be dating Neighbours star, Harley Bonner.
But model Natalie Roser put her love life aside on Thursday, and was busy working on her tan.
The 26-year-old positively glowed as she relaxed poolside in Los Angeles, smiling as she soaked up some sunny rays.
Radiant: Aussie model Natalie Roser glowed as she posed poolside in a black and white bikini on Thursday
Putting her toned tummy on display, she showcased her incredible abs and enviable, slender pins.
She wore a checked black and white bandeau bikini from her very own swimsuit line.
Accessorising with a black cap and no jewellery, the bare-face beauty kept it simple, drawing attention to her striking features and flawless complexion.
Her luscious blonde tresses hung in waves over her chest as she smiled for the camera.
Classic: The blonde beauty wore a checked bandeau bikini from her very own swimsuit line
The star shared the image with her 755,000 Instagram followers, captioning the moment 'LA is weather #goals today! I'll be wearing my cute @roserthelabel bikini all day'
The lazy day was in contrast to her activities Wednesday, when the model posted a photo of herself working up a sweat during an intense session at the gym.
Sporting a black singlet and workout shorts, Natalie pulled her long locks to the side, playfully joking 'I don't know why I bother washing my hair'.
Favourite piece: Natalie wore the bikini in different ways, wearing denim shorts with the bathers when she posed in them beachside
Hitting the gym: The lazy day was in contrast to Natalie's activities Wednesday, when the model posted a photo of herself working up a sweat during an intense session at the gym.
The young model moved to the Los Angeles earlier this year to pursue a modelling career after her shock-split from fiance, Dan.
It didn't take Natalie too long to find love again though, with rumours swirling last month about a new beau when Neighbours star Harley posted a picture of the two together for Valentine's Day.
On Tuesday, the actor posted another picture with the blonde bombshell, captioning the moment 'Missing this beautiful creature. One month to go... Hurry up time, you big stupid idiot head.'
New beau: Natalie and former fiance Dan Adair broke off their engagement last year, with the former Miss Universe contestant seen cosying up to Neighbours star, Harley Bonner
